2 FREEZER


This version features a freezer option ( both mouse batons and 'F' 

key pressed together ) this will halt the program in operation 

and take you to the action replay main function menu .

 
Freeze function will work on majority of programs but you can 

find some programs can not be frozzen dew to their construction.


Pressing 'HELP' will produce an on screen list of all the commands

available 'SHIFT' will pose the listing .

 
FREEZER COMMANDS 


F1 			clears the actual picture
F2 			puts cursor in the top lefthand corner
F9			Keyboard setting US/German
F10			switch screens
HELP		short help listing (shift to pause)
DEL			clears the char at cursor position
Back Space	clear the char. in front of the cursor position
TAB			inserts a space in front of the cursor
KEYS

X 			will return to the program in memory
XX			switches out the catrige ( to return to AR is to 				loaded it again)


