5 TRAINER

TS value

starts trainer and searches for the first value eg lives TS4 or TS!4 for dec value then go back to the game get killed and freeze the program and then do this

! dec 
% binary
nothing in front for hex

T value

continues trainer with notified value ( after the kill eg T3 or T!3 for dec value "

TX 

will exit the trainer

if the trainer is successful you will receive address to change the live or what ever you are looking for 

M address

eg  14444  03 00 66 77 88 55 78 87 ghfdt p;,jmn

change the firs two bytes so it looks like that 

14444 FF 00 66 77 88 55 78 87 ghft p,jmn

now you have 256 lives 

some programs use binary coded decimal for representation so dont be fulled

others like Interceptor (use no fast mem) use hex 24 to store 2 sidewinders

and 4 mavricks that was a pain to find. (13 places foward is the acceleration

factor 7f maximum 80 reverse it is fun try it!!) Look close to the adress 

for energy or other weapons. You can use FA - find adress but make sure that 

it is even this will give you all the adresses dealing that adress and by

changing them you can make unlimited lifes EVEN LAMER can do it with some

knowledge of 68000.

